00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:12.000
categories coming — A-I AirPods, smart glasses, a wearable pendant,

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:16.000
a HomePad, a tabletop robot, and a security camera. Ternus

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:20.000
is inheriting a denser pipeline than the public narrative suggests.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:24.000
Alex Kelley's ten-fifty-eight A-M ping yesterday is unreplied — one

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:28.000
paragraph closes the Cook-letter, Vergecast, and Gurman loops at once.

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:32.000
Local. Rep. Brad Christ did not attend Governor Kehoe's signing

