00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:48.000
City — storms rolled through before sunrise. Mostly sunny, high

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:52.000
near seventy-eight. Pippa walk before ten A-M. Messages — who's

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:56.000
